12... Kh8 { Black prepares ...f6 to cover the pawn. } 13. Nc4 f6 14. d4
{ This the point we open the position now so that Black's weaknesses are more exposed. This looks uncomfortable for Black to play. It's a tough call between this approach and the pawn grab on move 12 - choose according to your taste. }
