{ Our moves are all natural and increase pressure, step by step. This position has been tested in GM games frequently, with good results for White. After Black's most popular reply @@StartBracket@@developing the knight to a6@@EndBracket@@, I want to show an interesting idea. }
13... Na6 { Black wants to transfer the knight to e6, a good idea. } 14. h4
