1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. Bb5+ Bd7 4. Bxd7+ Nxd7
{ Black takes with the knight, which leads to different positions than the queen recapture. The key point is that we shouldn't commit to a pawn formation quickly - more on this topic after our next move. }
