{ The move  6...Nc6  is covered via the move order @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pp3ppp/8/2pp4/3P4/2P2N2/PP3PPP/RNBQKB1R b KQkq d3 0 5@@EndFEN@@  5...Nc6  6.Bb5  Nf6  and a welcome sight. }
