{ Now we have reached a position that only arises from the French Tarrasch but also the Sicilian. We play the following line: @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1.e4  c5  2.Nf3  e6  3.c3  d5  4.exd5  exd5  5.d4  Nc6  6.Bb5  Bd6  7.O-O  Nge7  8.dxc5  Bxc5  9.Nbd2  O-O  10.Nb3  Bb6  , when we reach the position currently on the board. }
